{"tid":1132378,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！steam註冊用戶突破十億！","createTime":"2019-04-30T09:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T11:43:28.000Z","uid":33359,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5f287d6c0dead969826b52bb5f5993aac53f5903","tid":1132378,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"STEAM 服務穩定而完整<br />\n<br />\n根據 techraptor 報導，從 2003 年 9 月推出的 Steam 遊戲服務平台，在前天（28日）<br />\n達到了十億個用戶，Steam ID 搜尋網站 顯示，4 月 28 日的  amusedsilentdragonfly<br />\n這個帳號 ID ，就是第十億個帳號，雖然沒有什麼第十億用戶大獎終身免費之類的，這十<br />\n億之中也可能有一些多重帳號、閒置帳號甚至詐騙帳號存在，但是這個仍然可以被視為一<br />\n個重要的里程碑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/JV2SGIu.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJV2SGIu.png&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1bO6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=7846de0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/JV2SGIu.png</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年的遊戲發展會議重點，Steam 對於未來成長仍然非常看好<br />\n<br />\nSteam 官方在之前就有發佈過關於自身平台的相關數據統整，包括每月登入人數達 9000<br />\n萬、同時最高在線人數達 1850 萬等等，都是在跟其他平台如 PSN 數位服務 等對手比拼<br />\n，這是一場數據平台戰爭。在今年的發展重點中，也提到提升更多遊戲庫界面新設計、更<br />\n多平台不只 VR ，包括主機甚至手機版本的 Steam 工作坊開發系統，讓有心發展的開發<br />\n人員有更多機會一展長才。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/8HSdKYd.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8HSdKYd.jpg&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1bO6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=7dc1bcd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/8HSdKYd.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSteam 網咖許可計畫（Steam PC Caf&eacute; Program）<br />\n<br />\n在使用者組成部分，Steam 網咖許可計畫（Steam PC Caf&eacute; Program）也讓他們穩固了非<br />\n常大量的亞洲客戶，比起其他洲的客群，亞洲玩家更傾向於在網咖遊玩 Steam 遊戲，《<br />\n絕地求生》的發展也是因此受惠。<br />\n<br />\n在市場發展上有趣的是，Steam主要的付費方式，包括多項信用卡、電信帳單等五款付費<br />\n方式，在亞洲市場只有 12.5% 的使用程度，超過八成是使用這些非主要付費方式，包括<br />\n Steam 蒸氣卡或者當地代理公司的其他點數卡轉費等，官方也承諾將支援更多付費方式<br />\n與優惠兌率，讓玩家能保有最等值的交易。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Steam/M.1556600052.A.562.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FSteam%2FM.1556600052.A.562.html&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1bO6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=54218f1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Steam/M.1556600052.A.562.html</a>"},{"pid":"0c23dbea5b3e3a30f8cb59c1df6ff435262b6b4b","tid":1132378,"uid":65201,"like":1,"dislike":34,"score":-33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:11:58.000Z","msg":"識用一定係用epic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63acbd357dd0349950e0f33a3b699268048550de","tid":1132378,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c23dbea5b3e3a30f8cb59c1df6ff435262b6b4b","tid":1132378,"uid":65201,"like":1,"dislike":34,"score":-33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:11:58.000Z","msg":"識用一定係用epic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:15:05.000Z","msg":"Epic世一"},{"pid":"977c9cd99e63f26a5ac11aed458778bfd6cd5d07","tid":1132378,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5923a7c6d535a5d319f3521fd3129261cd6d0cd0","tid":1132378,"uid":65201,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"63acbd357dd0349950e0f33a3b699268048550de","tid":1132378,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c23dbea5b3e3a30f8cb59c1df6ff435262b6b4b","tid":1132378,"uid":65201,"like":1,"dislike":34,"score":-33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:11:58.000Z","msg":"識用一定係用epic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agre